Fed’s Bernanke Says Congress Needs to Address Long Term Deficit

-- B y   V i n c e   G o l l e
-- 
2011-06-22T19:01:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/fed-s-bernanke-says-congress-needs-to-address-long-term-deficit.html
Federal Reserve Chairman  Ben S.
Bernanke  said today that it’s urgent for U.S. lawmakers to
address the growing budget deficit of the world’s largest
economy.  “In my role as someone interested in financial stability,
addressing the medium- to long-term deficit is extremely
important,” Bernanke said at a press conference in  Washington .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vince Golle at 
 vgolle@bloomberg.net  